<p dir="auto"><a href="https://github.com/csstools/postcss-plugins/tree/main/plugins/postcss-pseudo-class-any-link">PostCSS Pseudo Class Any Link</a> lets you <code>:any-link</code> pseudo-class in CSS,
following the <a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/selectors-4/#the-any-link-pseudo" rel="nofollow">Selectors</a> specification.</p>
<div class="highlight highlight-source-postcss notranslate position-relative overflow-auto" dir="auto" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content="nav :any-link &gt; span {
